<div class="motto-strip">
  <span class="star"></span>
  <p>On Earth We Rise</p>
  <span class="star"></span>
</div>
<div class="main-wrap">
  <main class="content">
<div class="anthem-intro">
  <span class="anthem-tag">School Anthem</span>
  <h2>On Earth We Rise</h2>
  <p>The voice of Moi High School Kabarak sung at assemblies, celebrations, and ceremonies as a reminder of who we are and where we're going.</p>
</div>

<div class="verse">
  <span class="verse-label">Verse 1</span>
  <div class="verse-text">On Earth we rise, like a city on the mountain
<em>O yes, like a city on a mountain</em>
Taking up the challenge being seen across the world
<em>O yes, being seen right across the world</em>
We aim at the sun and we know we'll reach the top
<em>O yes, we know we'll reach the top</em>
And with God on our side, we know the sky is the limit
<em>O yes, the sky is the limit</em>
Now let us rise, and shine
Let's work even harder than now
Yes, let us rise and shine
We are the best cause we trust in the Lord</div>
</div>

<div class="verse">
  <span class="verse-label">Verse 2</span>
  <div class="verse-text">The Christian faith that holds us together
<em>O yes, it holds us together</em>
Teaching us good morals within Christianity
<em>O yes, within Christianity</em>
Invigorates when weary, and sanctions our happy times
<em>O yes, it sanctions our happy times</em>
Lays foundations of life, and gives us hope on earth
<em>O yes, it gives us hope on earth</em></div>
</div>

<div class="verse">
  <span class="verse-label">Verse 3</span>
  <div class="verse-text">We thank the Lord, for the Founder of Kabarak
<em>O yes, for the Founder of Kabarak</em>
Taking the decision for the benefit of Kenyan youths
<em>O yes, for the benefit of Kenyan youths</em>
Generations of the youth will always be grateful
<em>O yes, they will always be grateful</em>
We pray that Kabarak be a burning spear forever
<em>O yes, be a burning spear</em>
Forever.</div>
</div>

<div class="author-card">
  <div class="label">Composed by</div>
  <div class="name">David Zalo Okuku</div>
  <div class="signature"></div>
</div>
